modName: Vampire chain cuirass CBBE DG UNP UNPBBBP no HDT high heels - DELETED
summary: light skimpy set, doesn't require HDT high heels
descriptionHtml:
Vampire chain cuirass is light armor craftable in leather.
Has boots, cuirass, pauldrons, gloves craftable in leather; circlets and wings craftable in jewellery. 
7 color variants goldred, goldblue, steelblack, copperblack, coppergreen, ironred, copperwhite. 

doesn't require HDT high heels (file with HDT high heel boots is [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/69488]here[/url])

PS. As for me, I prefer version with HDT high heels - it looks more elegant

You can make anything what you want while it is non-commercial destribution and you give me credits as original mod author.
I don't give permission to upload it in steam. 


Credits:
